            . I went up to the Market-house to see what it was o'clock, I heard something make a noise, I peeped through, and saw the prisoner sitting in the hay lost, with the box in his hand telling the money, and saw a hole made out of the lost into the prisoner's room. I called to some of my fellow workmen, and took him.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in his defence.</p>
